{"tid":1142920,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"MA-1係一件咩年齡層都啱著嘅外套","createTime":"2019-05-07T11:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T08:03:02.000Z","uid":227650,"like":14,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9288e51387fb8322aaa363de085c89c57230d6","tid":1142920,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"後生仔適合:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLWikPs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLWikPs.jpg&h=4af2df5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女仔適合，而且女仔著會有另一種味道。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hY7EPCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhY7EPCZ.jpg&h=396624fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOJgRRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOJgRRm.jpg&h=2c3c15c6&s={SIZE}\" /> 中年成熟男人適合(而且係我個人覺得最適合著嘅一個年齡層)。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Cm6uDG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Cm6uDG.jpg&h=d925f23e&s={SIZE}\" />小朋友著亦都好適合，仲幾cute添！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o9S12ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo9S12ZE.jpg&h=471d2184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都話ma-1係公廁褸、冬天一個招牌砸死好多人。但我反而想喺另一個角度睇，ma-1係一件經典、易襯嘅褸;所以多人著係好正常，亦都唔使話佢公廁。"},{"pid":"658948fc08db655f3f37e1785c755d4b2911c88d","tid":1142920,"uid":142313,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔邊會睇咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />照鏡已經知買唔買好"},{"pid":"b8ac6f11e8daa50a1d42e241e725b0374fe7254d","tid":1142920,"uid":142383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"圖文不符"},{"pid":"ab728ae4a2721f6a0faf3c2f197276a9e16ab535","tid":1142920,"uid":227650,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658948fc08db655f3f37e1785c755d4b2911c88d","tid":1142920,"uid":142313,"like":17,"d